Name: UnitTypeName
Description: Name of the UnitType using the DDI Name structure.

Name: Label
Description: A display label for the UnitType. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the UnitType. May be expressed in multiple languages and supports the use of structured content.

Name: ConceptReference
Description: Reference to the Concept that defines the UnitType. TypeOfObject should be set to Concept.
